明显破坏，比如半夜经常醒来，这种情况对身体的影响就不是特别大。」孟繁强说，每个人的睡眠需求不一样，多数成年人只需要睡 7 个小时左右。好睡眠最主要的一个判断标准是看起床后是否感觉精神饱满、体力恢复，而非单纯看时长。 来源：中国新闻网晚睡晚起睡够时长算熬夜吗 _ 睡眠 _ 孟繁强 _ 成年人"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-5e8206be2b2b6a0fea7219c3716e0af1_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "53 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/640980407"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI8Z+rsJGY7I9fEAMaCTEwNDcxNzk2OCDe+MKtBjAAOO0HQA5yCTY0MDk4MDQwN3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1706150018.82117", "card_id": "Q_530936571", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 29}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "同为五小强，为什么一辉常态能打三巨头，其他四人和三巨头差距那么大？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "一辉在常态下打败艾亚哥斯，但是其他四人还打不过其他天字辈冥斗士之前差距也没这么大啊"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-264fd20dd8c5fc2f0d0347f800957992_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "45 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/530936571"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I8Z+rsJGY7I9fEAMaCDgwMjY4MjIwINLluZMGMAA4NUAPcgk1MzA5MzY1NzF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1706150018.82675", "card_id": "Q_640609219", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 50}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价游戏《幻兽帕鲁》？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "steam 销售三百万份，在线人数百万人，如何评价这一现象？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-7d82a01710952af58b7893898fff7af9_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "40 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/640609219"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8Z+rsJGY7I9fEAMaCTEwNDYzNTY0NiDZi7etBjAAOF